# New Story — BurnProof-AgentFlow

Create a new story file using `templates/story-template.md`.

Ask the human for: Epic ID, story title, domain (FE/BE/FS), user story statement, and acceptance criteria. Then create the file at `specs/stories/STORY-[EPIC-ID]-[N]-[kebab-title].md` with all fields pre-filled.

Remind the human to add test levels to each AC before assigning to a dev agent.
